## Webhook Security

```typescript
// All outbound webhooks are signed:
const signature = await crypto.subtle.sign(
  'HMAC',
  await importKey(webhookSecret),
  new TextEncoder().encode(rawBody)
);
const hexSignature = bufferToHex(signature);
// Header: X-GeoP-Signature: sha256={hexSignature}

